0.2.name: wordpress/screencastcom-video-embedder
0.2.description: Screencast.com Video Embedder is a plugin that allows Screencast.com users an easy way to embed their content into their WordPress Blog or Website. Just enter the shortcode [screencast url="SCREENCAST SHORT URL" width="WIDTH" height="HEIGHT"] into your post or page and let the plugin do the rest!
